Immediately after the incident, I recognized the gravity of what I had done and acted swiftly to ensure the victim's safety and wellbeing. Understanding the severity of the situation, I promptly took him to the nearest emergency room to receive the necessary medical attention.

This incident is completely out of character for me and stands as an isolated occurrence in an otherwise law-abiding life. I deeply regret the harm I have caused and the impact it has had on the victim's life and their loved ones.

Your Honour, I plead guilty and accept the gravity of my actions. I respectfully request your leniency and consideration in determining an appropriate sentence. I am fully prepared to face the consequences of my actions.

Thank you for your attention.

